.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, cranberry, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, traveling, collecting
4 different pets are kept: goat, bird, goldfish, mouse
1. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the owner of the goat is the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
7. the person eating raspberry is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | cranberry   | raspberry      | broccoli       | apple |
| Hobby   | hiking | collecting | traveling     | reading |
| Pet     | mouse     | bird  | goat | goldfish |

