.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, juice, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, animation, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, frog, rabbit
1. the owner of the frog is the person watching spy movies##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the person watching fantasy movies and the owner of the dog##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person drinking water##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | mirinda          | water | iced-tea        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | thriller | fantasy   | spy     |
| Pet           | dog | mouse         | rabbit         | frog |

