.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, traveling, hiking, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher, engineer, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, punk, techno, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the engineer is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the writer is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of punk is between the police-officer and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the engineer##3
7. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | writing      | hiking       | board-games    |
| Job           | teacher  | engineer  | writer | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | techno | punk         | hip-hop    |

