.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, juice, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, designer, librarian, writer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, badminton, tea-polo
1. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
6. the person who's sport is tea-polo is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the dressmaker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
9. the writer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | milk         | mirinda  | juice     | tea         |
| Job        | writer | designer | dressmaker | librarian         |
| Sport      | climbing         | badminton  | rowing   | tea-polo |

