.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, blues, house
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indonesian, indian, dutch
4 different pets are kept: frog, fish, ferret, pony
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 2. the german is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the indian is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of ambient##2
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the fan of blues##1
 7. the dutch is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
 9. the indonesian is between the fan of house and the fan of blues##2
10. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | blues    | hip-hop | house    |
| Nationality   | german | indian | indonesian  | dutch |
| Pet           | ferret   | pony    | frog        | fish   |

