.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, coffee, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, police-officer, dancer, accountant
There are 4 different nationalities: french, turkish, german, argentine
1. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the police-officer is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the argentine is on the left or right of the dancer##3
4. the police-officer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the police-officer##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the turkish##3
9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | tea                | iced-tea  | lemonade | coffee   |
| Job           | accountant | police-officer | entrepreneur   | dancer |
| Nationality   | turkish         | french     | argentine     | german |

