.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, plum, grapefruit, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, time-travel, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, ambient, funk
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the fan of folk is between the person watching horror movies and the fan of funk##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | grapefruit    | plum  | grapes  | spinach |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy | drama | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | folk     | funk    | gospel |

