.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, milk, water
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, mexican, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, dog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the cat is between the person drinking milk and the indonesian##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the mexican is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the indian##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the indonesian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
8. the mexican is the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the nigerian is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | milk      | cola  | water    |
| Nationality   | mexican   | indian | nigerian | indonesian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig      | dog       | cat   | snake      |

