There are 4 different nationalities: german, spanish, italian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, basketball, badminton
1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the malaysian is between the person who's sport is baseball and the german##2
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | chess | sudoku  | gardening  |
| Nationality   | italian | spanish       | malaysian | german |
| Sport         | basketball   | baseball      | badminton | climbing       |

