The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon, cycling, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, van, subway
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person driving the ship and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
