.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, asparagus, papaya, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, dancing, skydiving, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, rat, cat
1. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | papaya    | asparagus    | cabbage  | apricot |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | dancing | chess | skydiving      |
| Pet     | goat   | dog        | cat   | rat       |

 